<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Roadsidely</title>
  <META NAME="Description" CONTENT="Build Relationships, Not Spreadsheets with CRM for PR and Social Media Professionals.">
  <meta property="og:image" content=""/>
  <meta property="og:url" content="http://www.pressrm.com/"/>
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="PressRM - CRM for PR and Social Pros"/>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,700,600' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

  <style style="text/css">
  html, body {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  #full-screen-background-image {
    z-index: -999;
    min-height: 100%;
    min-width: 1200px;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }
  body {
    padding-top: 50px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,h4 {
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .text {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    line-height: 120%;
  }
  .closing,.closing a {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: .6;
  }
  .form-control {
    font-size: 28px;
    padding: 24px;
    padding-left: 15px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0px;
  }
  .btn.signup {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-top: 19px;
    padding-top: 4px;
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 0px;
    border: none;
    background-color: #00b64f;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn.share {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .btn.twitter {
    background-color: #4099ff;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn.facebook {
    background-color: #3b5998;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn.googleplus {
    background-color: #d94834;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn.linkedin {
    background-color: #007bb6;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
  }
  .logo1 {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .logo2 {
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <img alt="full screen background image" src="/assets/background-dark.jpg" id="full-screen-background-image" /> 
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 text-center"><span class="logo1">Roadside</span><span class="logo2">ly</span><p class="lead">on demand roadside assistance from your smartphone</p></div>
  </div>

  <%= yield %>
  <br /><br /><br />
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4"><p class="lead">Quickly summon roadside service by selecting your location on the map.</p></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4"><p class="lead">See exactly where the service vehicle is and when it will be arriving. No more wondering.</p></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4"><p class="lead">We handle the payment with the service providers so there's no surprises or tips to worry about.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row text-center text-center" style="margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">
    <div class="col-lg-2 col-lg-offset-1">
          LOCKOUTS
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-2">
          GAS DELIVERY
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-2">
          JUMPSTARTS
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-2">
          TIRE CHANGES
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-2">
          TOWS
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2"><h3>All this and more for a monthly rate that's <u>less than AAA</u>.</h3></div>
  </div>



  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
      <p class="closing">hello@roadsidely.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
